"dbe14ba527fa4db7bc2e9e7a943ce059"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HWh4ThaGayw?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p> Chinese Room 是这样描述这款游戏的：“灾难袭击了苏格兰海岸外的 Beira D 石油钻井平台。在坍塌的钻井平台上航行，将你的船员从所有逻辑和现实边缘的超凡脱俗的恐怖中解救出来。”</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> <em>Still Wakes the Deep</em>将于 2024 年初登陆 Xbox Series X/S、PlayStation 5、PC 和 Game Pass。</p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/sgf-2023"><em>在这里</em></a><em>了解夏季游戏节的所有新闻</em><em>！</em></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/the-dear-esther-studio-is-building-an-oil-rig-horror-game-still-wakes-the-deep-184802111.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-dear-esther-studio-is-building-an-oil-rig-horror-game-still-wakes-the-deep-184802111.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9732975b-eb47-4b07-886a-f62094b8e4a7</guid><dc:creator>杰西卡·康迪特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Sun, 11 Jun 2023 18:48:02 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686509285</ingested><modified> 2023-06-11T18:48:08+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jessica Conditt]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/b1f366b0-0887-11ee-bbef-99aa416d51e9" width="1919"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title>